basestation

Class BaseStation

  • java.lang.Object
    • basestation.BaseStation

  • public class BaseStation
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains logic to manage and unify input and output between bots and vision sources. This class is a singleton to prevent accidental BaseStation duplication.

    • Method Summary
